features: ⚙️【Wide Angle Front and Rear Dash Cam】This dual dash cam has a 4K resolution front camera and a waterproof rear camera. The front camera captures the license plates and road signs clearly even at night, thus ensuring to get you the best footage. Wide-angle front (170°) and rear（140°） cameras help eliminate the blind spots in your vision.

⚙️【4K Full HD Day and Night Recording】3-inch IPS screen car camera with 32GB SD card can work infinitely with a loop recording function. A dual rotatable wide viewing lens can clearly record every detail of your driving in 4K FHD resolution. F2.0 large aperture, WDR, Eliminates the need for an auxiliary light source even in low-light environments, making it easy to obtain sharp, color-accurate images.

⚙️【Emergency Video Lock and Loop Recording】 With G-sensor turned on, when the camera detects a collision or vibration, it will automatically lock the video being recorded. Locked video will not be overwritten by loop recording. The Loop Recording function automatically overwrites past unlocked videos to free up more space for new videos. The 32GB MicroSD card can usually be recorded for a week. 【🔧Note: 32GB memory card is included, no need to buy it separately】

⚙️【24/7 Parking Guard】When the car engine and camera are both off if the parking guard is on, the camera will automatically start recording when it detects vibration and collision, lock a video, and then automatically shut down. If a dash and cabin cam is required to protect your vehicle 24/7, an additional hard-wired kit must be installed, eliminating the need to open the parking guard. 【🔧Note: Additional hardware kits need to be purchased separately】

⚙️【Easy Installation & Easy to use 】 This dash cam front and inside is very easy to install and operate with reference pictures in our user manual. Connect the dash cam with the suction mount (included) and attach it to your windshield. Insert an SD card (32GB memory card included) and connect to the power supply. The car dash camera will start recording immediately after igniting. Meantime, you can playback videos of each clear detail on the car dash cam.

⚙️【Professional After s support】The dash cams combined with loop recording, G-sensor, and motion detection functions, you never lose any crucial evidence. We offer 7*24 hours of technical support. If you have any queries, please feel free to contact us.
